      "text": "In case you missed it: as part of the 21st Century ROAD to Housing Act, we passed legislation to stop Wall Street from buying up Nevadans’ homes and raising costs. Now, I’m proud to say it’s the law of the land. https://t.co/KZKSz26pXR",
