      "text": "We’ve seen this play out time and again in Nevada: when Donald Trump loses, it’s “rigged.” But when he wins, all of a sudden it’s not rigged.\n\nHe doesn’t care about actual election security or preventing fraud – our elections in Nevada are already safe and secure. Trump wants to",
